Paging Godfather: % of body fat seems to not be working correctly. The graph shows a flat line, and the data pages show the same number for all data points.Hopers, I've found that staying good during the week and relaxing standards on the weekend is a good way to keep eating relatively under control. Normally I'm fairly strict on weekdays. On weekends I usually relax a bit on one day (a bit of bread for a breakfast sandwich? Fine!), and stop giving a fuck the other (I WILL EAT ANYTHING!). Makes social activities much easier, especially if you coordinate the fuck-all day with an unlimited mimosa brunch Hopers
